<title>HONG KONG: C.Lyonnais sets warrants on Hopewell.</title>
<headline>C.Lyonnais sets warrants on Hopewell.</headline>
<dateline>HONG KONG 1997-02-17</dateline>
<text>
<p>Credit Lyonnais Financial Products (Guernsey) Ltd said on Monday it issued 800 million American-style call warrants on Hopewell Holdings Ltd.</p>
<p>Ten warrants control one share.</p>
<p> STRIKE PRICE   HK$4.82	   PREMIUM	20.55 PCT</p>
<p> ISSUE PRICE    HK$0.0625	 GEARING	7.24X</p>
<p> EXPIRATION     25.NOV.97	 BOARD LOT    10,000</p>
<p>LISTING</p>
<p>HONG KONG PAY DATE 04.MAR.97</p>
<p> SPOT PRICE     HK$4.525	  LISTING DATE 06.MAR.97</p>
<p> SETTLEMENT     CASH SETTLEMENT OR PHYSICAL DELIVERY</p>
<p>-- Hong Kong Newsroom (852) 2843 6441</p>
</text>
